laboratory_examinations.findings: Negative for Neisseria gonorrhoeae. Validated for use on urine samples.
A 1.4 x 1.4 cm T2 hyperintense lesion consistent with a cyst or biliary hamartoma; mildly dilated appendix measuring 7.7 mm; mild hydronephrosis of the right kidney. No ascites or lymphadenopathy.
